%20'peak%20demand'%20for%20oil%20sometime%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Huber.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20always%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20diversify%20one's%20economy%20away%20from%20just%20oil%20but%20now%20more%20than%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f0b0eb00-b6b7-4f2f-9acd-d2d555ca6010%5C%22%3EThe%20role%20of%20OPEC%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20changing%20dynamics%20of%20oil%20also%20sharpens%20the%20long-standing%20question%20of%20OPEC's%20influence%20and%20relevance.%20The%20oil%20producer%20group%20led%20by%20Saudi%20Arabia%20accounts%20for%20about%2030%25%20of%20global%20crude%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20goes%20in%20cycles.%20They%20were%20obviously%20relevant%20in%20the%201970s%20when%20they%20were%20able%20to%20increase%20prices%20almost%20single-handedly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Huber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20problem%20is%20when%20oil%20prices%20spike%2C%20it%20sends%20oil%20companies%20searching%20for%20temporarily%20profitable%20oil%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20US%20shale%20boom%20as%20the%20most%20recent%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOPEC%20also%20faces%20rifts%20within%20its%20members%2C%20who%20have%20competing%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20question%20now%20is%20whether%20OPEC%20members%20are%20all%20aligned%20in%20terms%20of%20oil%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20The%20Geopolitical%20Business's%20Prakash%2C%20who%20added%20that%20not%20all%20OPEC%20members%20may%20be%20on%20board%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20plan%20to%20boost%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20potential%20Trump%20presidency%20in%20the%20US%20could%20drive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-election-impact-trump-win-election-financials-energy-rbc-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edomestic%20oil%20and%20gas%20production.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20OPEC%20can't%20bring%20everybody%20together%2C%20and%20members%20go%20their%20separate%20ways%2C%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20further%20polarization%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Prakash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20energy%20bringing%20the%20region%20together%2C%20like%20it%20did%20in%20the%20past%2C%20energy%20coupled%20with%20geopolitics%20could%20fragment%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmajor-oil-producers-saudi-arabia-russia-diversify-economies-opec-shale-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729565013000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6716f1daa0a0cc14f222deb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmajor-oil-producers-saudi-arabia-russia-diversify-economies-opec-shale-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20has%20witnessed%20a%20massive%20rise%20in%20oil%20production%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years%20amid%20the%20shale%20boom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmajor-oil-producers-saudi-arabia-russia-diversify-economies-opec-shale-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Zyada%20hero%20ban%20raha%20hai%E2%80%99%3A%20Rohit%20targets%20NZ%20batter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729564756000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114444461%2Cimgsize-50628.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnew-zealand-in-india%2Fzyada-hero-baan-raha-hai-woh-rohit-sharma-targets-nz-batter-with-hilarious-stump-mic-chatter%2Farticleshow%2F114444170.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20India's%20defeat%20to%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20humorous%20comment%20by%20Indian%20captain%20Rohi