o%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%2C%20the%20bunker%20contained%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20cash%20and%20gold%2C%20allegedly%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20group's%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20disclosure%20followed%20a%20series%20of%20targeted%20airstrikes%20conducted%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20on%20Sunday%20night%2C%20aimed%20at%20Hezbollah's%20financial%20assets.%20IDF%20spokesperson%20Rear%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari%20provided%20detailed%20information%20during%20a%20televised%20briefing%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BTonight%2C%20I%20am%20going%20to%20declassify%20intelligence%20on%20a%20site%20that%20we%20did%20not%20strike-where%20Hezbollah%20has%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20gold%20and%20cash%20in%20Hassan%20Nasrallah's%20bunker.%20The%20bunker%20is%20located%20directly%20under%20Al-Sahel%20Hospital%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Beirut.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CTonight%2C%20I%20am%20going%20to%20declassify%20intelligence%20on%20a%20site%20that%20we%20did%20not%20strike%E2%80%94where%20Hezbollah%20has%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20gold%20and%20cash%E2%80%94in%20Hassan%20Nasrallah's%20bunker.%20Where%20is%20the%20bunker%20located%3F%20Directly%20under%20Al-Sahel%20Hospital%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Beirut.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnListen%20to%20IDF%20Spox.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSjMZQpKqoJ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSjMZQpKqoJ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(%40IDF)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIDF%2Fstatus%2F1848436265143677104%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHagari%20said%20that%20the%20site%20had%20not%20been%20struck%20yet%2C%20despite%20the%20alleged%20presence%20of%20significant%20financial%20resources.%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20estimates%2C%20there%20is%20at%20least%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars%20in%20dollar%20bills%20and%20gold%20stored%20in%20this%20bunker.%20This%20money%20could%20and%20still%20can%20be%20used%20to%20rebuild%20the%20state%20of%20Lebanon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunday%20night's%20airstrikes%20targeted%20nearly%2030%20Hezbollah-linked%20locations%2C%20including%20sites%20operated%20by%20Al-Qard%20Al-Hassan%20(AQAH)%2C%20a%20financial%20firm%20linked%20to%20Hezbollah.%20AQAH%2C%20though%20registered%20as%20a%20charity%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20both%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20States%20of%20serving%20as%20a%20critical%20financial%20arm%20of%20Hezbollah%2C%20facilitating%20its%20access%20to%20cash%20and%20gold%20reserves%20for%20military%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHagari%20claimed%20that%20one%20of%20the%20key%20targets%20was%20an%20underground%20vault%20containing%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20cash%20and%20gold%2C%20resources%20that%20were%20allegedly%20being%20used%20to%20fund%20attacks%20on%20Israel.%20While%20Hagari%20did%20not%20clarify%20whether%20all%20the%20funds%20were%20destroyed%20in%20the%20strike%2C%20he%20said%20that%20further%20airstrikes%20could%20be%20expected%2C%20particularly%20targeting%20additional%20financial%20hubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strikes%20followed%20an%20intensified%20Israeli%20effort%20to%20disrupt%20Hezbollah's%20finances.%20According%20to%20IDF%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Lt%20Gen%20Herzi%20Halevi%2C%20the%20campaign%20involved%20over%20300%20strikes%20on%20Hezbollah%20positions%20in%20Lebanon%20over%20a%2024-hour%20period%2C%20including%20critical%20financial%20and%20logistical%20hubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Qard%20Al-Hassan%20has%20operated%20in%20Lebanon%20since%20the%201980s%2C%20providing%20credit%20to%20Lebanese%20citizens%20in%20exchange%20for%20gold%20deposits.%20While%20officially%20classified%20as%20a%20charity%2C%20Israeli%20and%20US%20officials%20argue%20that%20the%20firm%20is%20a%20critical%20asset%20in%20Hezbollah's%20financial%20network%2C%20enabling%20the%20group%20to%20launder%20money%20and%20finance%20its%20activities%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20civilian%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lebanese%20people%20and%20the%20Iranian%20regime%20are%20Hezbollah's%20two%20main%20sources%20of%20income%2C%20Hagari%20claimed.%20He%20alleged%20that%20the%20financial%20mechanisms%20used%20by%20the%20group%2C%20which%20include%20cash%20transfers%20through%20Syria%20and%20gold%20smuggled%20into%20Lebanon%20via%20Iran.%20Factories%20operated%20by%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20Syria%2C%20Yemen%2C%20and%20Turkey%20are%20allegedly%20used%20to%20generate%20substantial%20income%20to%20support%20the%20group's%20terror%20activities%2C%20according%20to%20IDF%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20related%20development%2C%20Israel%20carried%20out%20an%20airstrike%20on%20Monday%20in%20Syria%2C%20targeting%20the%20head%20of%20Hezbollah's%20financial%20unit%2C%20known%20as%20Unit%204400.%20The%20unit%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20flow%20of%20Iranian%20funds%20to%20Hezbollah%2C%20primarily%20through%20proceeds%20from%20Tehran's%20oil%20sales.%20The%20unnamed%20commander%2C%20who%20had%20only%20been%20in%20the%20role%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20strike%2C%20according%20to%20Hagari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20the%20second%20significant%20assassination%20of%20a%20Hezbollah%20financial%20figure%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20In%20early%20October%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20killed%20Mohammed%20Jafar%20Ksir%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Sheikh%20Salah%2C%20the%20previous%20head%20of%20Hezbollah's%20financial%20operations.%20Ksir%20had%20long%20overseen%20the%20group's%20revenue%20streams%2C%20which%20have%20been%20integral%20to%20its%20military%20and%20political%20influence%20in%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20Israeli%20operations%20came%20amid%20an%20escalation%20in%20hostilities%20between%20Hezbollah%20and%20Israel%2C%20which%20have%20been%20ongoing%20since%20Hezbollah%20launched%20a%20series%20of%20attacks%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Hamas%20following%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20estimate%20that%20approximately%202%2C000%20Hezbollah%20fighters%20have%20been%20killed%20since%20the%20conflict%20widened%20in%20late%20September%202023.%20Hezbollah%20has%20retaliated%20with%20rocket%20attacks%20on%20Israeli%20towns%20and%20military%20positions%2C%20including%20a%20recent%20barrage%20aimed%20at%20an%20intelligence%20base%20near%20Tel%20Aviv.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729562280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fmacc8bs8_hezbollah-bunker-idf-_625x300_22_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hezbollah-hamas-israel-claims-it-found-500-million-in-secret-hezbollah-bunker-in-beirut-6843741%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20on%20Monday%20said%20it%20has%20declassified%20intelligence%20which%20claims%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20secret%20Hezbollah%20financial%20hub%20beneath%20a%20Beirut%20hospital.%20According%20to%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%2C%20the%20bunker%20contained%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20cash%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20Web%20Services%20CEO%20doubles%20down%20on%20RTO%20mandate%20saying%20it's%20far%20better%20for%20'innovation'%20and%20'speed%20of%20execution'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matt%20Garman%20sitting%20on%20stage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6716f98e9b3250dbbce90cbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223058%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAWS%20CEO%20Matt%20Garman%20said%20teams%20are%20more%20innovative%2