%20sex%20on%20him%2C%20but%20she%20resisted%20by%20hitting%20him%20in%20the%20neck%2C%20so%20he%20stopped.%20She%20then%20escaped%20the%20room%20and%20had%20her%20father%20pick%20her%20up%20from%20the%20party.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20assault%2C%20Plaintiff%20fell%20into%20a%20deep%20depression%20which%20continues%20to%20affect%20every%20facet%20of%20her%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiffs%20are%20not%20named%20in%20the%20court%20papers%2C%20but%20they%20are%20described%20as%20two%20men%20and%20three%20women%2C%20including%20the%20one%20who%20was%2013%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20alleged%20VMAs%20rape.%20One%20of%20the%20men%20and%20three%20women%20also%20accused%20Combs%20of%20drugging%20them.%20While%20one%20of%20the%20male%20accusers%20claimed%20he%20was%20drugged%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20both%20Combs%20and%20an%20unnamed%20celebrity%2C%20the%20other%20male%20accuser%20said%20Combs%20groped%20him%20at%20a%20Ciroc%20Vodka%20party%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Combs%20has%20denied%20all%20the%20charges%20against%20him.%20He%20is%20currently%20being%20held%20behind%20bars%20at%20Brooklyn's%20Metropolitan%20Detention%20Center%20after%20being%20denied%20bail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729560480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ff5t7ddf_sean-diddy-combs-reuters_625x300_03_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-rapper-sean-diddy-drugged-and-raped-13-year-old-girl-lawsuit-claims-6843642%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20federal%20custody%20following%20multiple%20charges%20of%20racketeering%20and%20sex%20trafficking%2C%20has%20now%20been%20accused%20of%20raping%20a%2013-year-old%20girl%20with%20the%20help%20of%20two%20other%20celebrities%20at%20a%202000%20MTV%20VMAs%20afterparty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2