ign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20DOJ%20going%20after%20someone%20for%20encouraging%20political%20participation%20may%20very%20well%20be%20a%20fight%20that%20someone%20like%20Elon%20Musk%20wants%2C%26quot%3B%20Alvarez%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20'Look%20at%20them%20coming%20after%20us.%20We're%20just%20trying%20to%20help%20people%20vote.%20We're%20just%20trying%20to%20get%20people%20registered%2C'%20right%3F%20That's%20a%20narrative%20there%20that%20at%20least%20sounds%20good%20in%20general.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20for%20Musk's%20America%20PAC%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20have%20met%20Musk's%20unusual%20gambit%20with%20a%20range%20of%20responses.%20Gov.%20Josh%20Shapiro%20of%20Pennsylvania%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20the%20billionaire%20businessman's%20spending%20raises%20%26quot%3Bserious%20questions%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20that%20law%20enforcement%20could%20take%20a%20look%20at.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Shapiro%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Gov.%20Tim%20Walz%20said%20in%20an%20appearance%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20View%26quot%3B%20on%20Monday%20that%20he'd%20%26quot%3Blet%20the%20lawyers%20decide%26quot%3B%20if%20what%20Musk%20is%20doing%20is%20legal%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20giveaways%20are%20what%20happens%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20you%20have%20no%20economic%20plan%20that's%20going%20to%20benefit%20the%20middle%20class.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-1-million-giveaway-legal-questions-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729545245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671656e6a0a0cc14f2228479%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-1-million-giveaway-legal-question