rked-at-mcdonalds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20at%20McDonald's%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20formative%20experience.%20The%20chain%20says%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.mcdonalds.com%2Fcorpmcd%2Fbest-first-job.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20in%20eight%3C%2Fa%3E%20Americans%20has%20worked%20at%20one%20of%20its%20restaurants%20at%20some%20point%20in%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20flippin'%20burgers%20at%20McDonald's%2C%20when%20I%20was%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20that%20big%20Hobart%20machine%20washing%20dishes%20or%20waiting%20tables%2C%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20myself%20as%20stuck%20in%20some%20station%20in%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Paul%20Ryan%20said%20when%20he%20was%20Mitt%20Romney's%20vice%20presidential%20nominee%20in%202012.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.yahoo.com%2Fblogs%2Fticket%2Fpaul-ryan-colorado-supporters-drive-truck-used-mcdonald-215354358.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERyan%20mentioned%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20McDonald's%20experience%20alongside%20his%20love%20of%20camping%20and%20truck%20ownership%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20relate%20to%20middle-income%20Americans%20during%20that%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDerek%20Giacomantonio%2C%20the%20franchisee%20who%20owns%20and%20operates%20the%20McDonald's%20restaurant%20where%20Trump%20appeared%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20a%20job%20at%20McDonald's%20is%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%20burgers%20and%20fries%2C%20but%20a%20meaningful%20pathway%20to%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most-visited%20retail%20establishments%20in%20America.%20About%2087%25%20of%20US%20households%20visited%20the%20chain%20at%20least%20once%20in%20the%2012%20months%20to%20June%2030%2C%20according%20to%20data%20provider%20Numerator.%20McDonald's%20has%20about%2013%2C500%20locations%20in%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company's%20latest%20annual%20filing%20with%20the%20SEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E