26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20Health%20Secretary%2C%20which%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20refused%20earlier%20as%20well%2C%20the%20doctors%20had%20said%20they%20had%20some%20documents%20to%20back%20the%20allegations%20of%20irregularities%20against%20NS%20Nigam.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20pointed%20out%20that%20no%20one%20can%20be%20called%20an%20%26quot%3Baccused%26quot%3B%20just%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandipta%20Chakraborty%2C%20the%20representative%20in%20the%20delegation%20from%20N.R.S.%20Medical%20College%20%26amp%3B%20Hospital%2C%20however%20countered%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20against%20whom%20there%20are%20complaints%20of%20irregularities%20can%20be%20grammatically%20termed%20as%20'accused'.%20That%20same%20person%20can%20be%20termed%20as%20'guilty'%20if%20his%20guilt%20is%20proved%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20IANS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2015-day%20hunger%20strike%20had%20seen%20many%20of%20the%20participating%20doctors%20fall%20ill%20and%20need%20medical%20attention.%20But%20their%20spot%20was%20immediately%20filled%20by%20other%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20face-off%20had%20continued%20through%20the%20state's%20biggest%20festival%2C%20Durga%20puja%2C%20and%20reached%20its%20lowest%20point%20when%20nine%20people%20--%20doctors%20and%20others%20--%20were%20detained%20for%20shouting%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20justice%26quot%3B%20slogans%20at%20a%20pandal.%20Days%20before%20the%20police%20had%20stopped%20the%20proposed%20%26quot%3BAbhaya%20Parikrama%26quot%3B%20rallies%20by%20doctors%20--%20meant%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20their%20protest%20--%20at%20puja%20pandals.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729532760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fq9ut12bg_kolkata-rape-murder-case_625x300_13_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%