0of%20Understanding%20(MoUs)%20with%20various%20industries%2C%20including%20the%20automotive%2C%20energy%2C%20IT%2C%20and%20construction%20sectors.%20%26quot%3BOur%20students%20work%20on%20real-time%20industry%20projects%2C%20go%20for%20internships%2C%20and%20gain%20practical%20exposure%20to%20what's%20happening%20in%20the%20business%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kodoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20fostering%20entrepreneurship%20among%20students%2C%20both%20Dr%20Shankar%20and%20Mr%20Kodoor%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20universities%20to%20move%20beyond%20just%20being%20centres%20of%20knowledge%20dissemination.%20%26quot%3BUniversities%20need%20to%20become%20knowledge%20creators%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kodoor%20noted%2C%20explaining%20that%20innovation%20is%20crucial%20for%20addressing%20emerging%20challenges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729528800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fq16jhp88_ndtv-world-summit_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fndtv-world-summit-experts-call-for-stronger-education-industry-links-to-combat-job-disruption-6841385%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20fostering%20entrepreneurship%20among%20students%2C%20the%20noted%20educationists%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20universities%20to%20move%20beyond%20just%20being%20centres%20of%20knowledge%20dissemination.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Surfer%20dies%20after%20'swordfish%20attack'%20in%20Indonesia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729526688000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F43b8%2Flive%2Fba6b4950-8fc4-11ef-be67-d3b2237ffc84.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fckgng8nm416o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Giulia%20Manfrini%2C%2036%2C%20was%20reportedly%20struck%20while%20surfing%20