%5C%22%3ERani%20prepares%20a%20range%20of%20innovative%20products%20%E2%80%94%20including%20dried%20jackfruit%2C%20dried%20jackfruit%20powder%2C%20frozen%20tender%20jackfruit.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20the%20training%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20jackfruits%20can%20be%20used%20to%20create%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281732%2Fkerala-homemaker-entrepreneur-jackfruit-pasta-burger-superfood-value-add%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evalue-added%20products%20%3C%2Fa%3Elike%20dried%20powder%20and%20pulp.%20With%20jackfruits%20easily%20available%20in%20abundance%20not%20only%20in%20my%20backyard%20but%20throughout%20the%20region%2C%20and%20with%20a%20dryer%20already%20at%20home%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20establish%20a%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20my%20perception%20of%20jackfruits%20changed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experimenting%20with%20jackfruit%20products%2C%20Rani%20established%20her%20place%20in%20the%20local%20market%20with%20the%20support%20of%20local%20officials.%20Through%20her%20brand%20Eden%20Jackfruit%20Products%2C%20Rani%20leveraged%20white%20labelling%20to%20bring%20high-quality%20jackfruit-based%20products%20to%20the%20market.%20Currently%2C%20she%20is%20focused%20on%20building%20a%20website%20and%20establishing%20a%20strong%20presence%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Rani%20sources%20jackfruits%20from%2020%20neighbours%2C%20paying%20them%20a%20fair%20price%20for%20their%20produce%20while%20employing%2010%20workers%20to%20help%20process%20the%20fruits.%20Through%20value-addition%2C%20Rani%20earns%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%208%20lakh%20in%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBalancing%20home%2C%20work%2C%20and%20entrepreneurial%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20her%20journey%20of%20becoming%20an%20entrepreneur%20from%20a%20homemaker%2C%20Rani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20childhood%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20loved%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%20Here%2C%20my%20day%20starts%20at%205%20am%2C%20and%20I%20manage%20all%20household%20responsibilities%20before%20devoting%20my%20day%20to%20overseeing%20the%20operations%20at%20the%20factory%20and%20working%20with%20Kudumbashree.%20The%20busy%20schedule%20keeps%20me%20motivated%2C%20and%20when%20I%20retire%20to%20bed%20at%20night%2C%20I%20sleep%20peacefully.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20unwavering%20dedication%20also%20inspires%20those%20around%20her%2C%20including%20her%20daughter%2C%20Ana.%20%E2%80%9CI%20admire%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20work%20ethic%20and%20entrepreneurial%20drive.%20At%2057%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20how%20she%20stays%20so%20motivated%20to%20do%20the%20work.%20Honestly%2C%20I%20marvel%20at%20her%20ability%20to%20multitask%20effortlessly.%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20her%20sit%20down%20for%20even%2010%20minutes%20at%20her%20unit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20relentless%20commitment%20and%20passion%20for%20her%20business%20motivated%20me%20to%20rejoin%20the%20workforce%20after%20my%20maternity%20leave.%20From%20her%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20learned%20the%20importance%20of%20financial%20independence%20and%20the%20freedom%20to%20make%20my%20own%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ana%2C%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20Deloitte.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhenever%20she%20visits%20home%2C%20Rani%20prepares%20her%20favourite%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337560%2Fkathalfy-founder-aman-chhabra-brings-jackfruit-ready-to-eat-product-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejackfruit%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20Ana%20proudly%20shares%20with%20her%20colleagues%20in%20Bengaluru.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20follows%20a%20unique%20way%20of%20drying%20the%20jackfruits.%20Then%2C%2